{"tid":1649561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人諗過民間/民記反邀林奠參加對話會?","createTime":"2019-10-12T17:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T15:10:11.000Z","uid":266878,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be88befd64687c9ca98b6d96f98b0a4a8d9478b4","tid":1649561,"uid":266878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"覺得咁樣我地無得輸，一來推到國際易，二來，林鄭參加與否都有得做佢：<br />\n<br />\n(1) 如果林鄭唔嚟，做大佢話佢拒絕對話，無諗過解決問題，後果自負<br />\n<br />\n(2) 林鄭嚟，傾乜都係三幅被，但係主要喺睇場外巴，如果黑警事前事後舉旗放tg,  咁個畫面會好壯觀<br />\n<br />\n(3) 林鄭嚟，傾唔埋但黑警無做乜嘢，用嚟令淺藍淺黃停止對政府嘅幻想<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傾下"},{"pid":"8faad9251bda0ef351b29e40af5e9f7c5b723035","tid":1649561,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"可以一戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/13/LF3aIk.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F13%2FLF3aIk.jpeg&h=17878901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/13/Kk7vDh.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F13%2FKk7vDh.jpeg&h=cea05508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e30ce5bb4318df8eb0f7d406562cdc89365131fc","tid":1649561,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"推到推翻政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2568c69dc4a06a863c28ab132ca6943c455b5df0","tid":1649561,"uid":266878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e30ce5bb4318df8eb0f7d406562cdc89365131fc","tid":1649561,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"推到推翻政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12